I"_<h1 id="freesk8-robogotchi">FreeSK8 Robogotchi</h1>

<p>The <a href="https://derelictrobot.com/collections/production/products/freesk8-robogotchi">FreeSK8 Robogotchi</a> is an advanced BLE Receiver, Datalogger, and core component of the FreeSK8 System.</p>

<p>Think of it like a blackbox flight recorder for your esk8 or LEV.</p>

<p>The Robogotchi brings Always-On Logging as a core feature with an asynchronous logging integration with our FreeSK8 Mobile App.</p>

<p>Ride now, Sync later.</p>

